主要翻译
 
converse # vi formal (talk, chat)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 谈话 tán huà TC Traditional Chinese 談話  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 交谈 tán huà，jiāo tán TC Traditional Chinese 交談 
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 谈天 tán huà，tán tiān 
 -- We only converse about once a month.
 
converse with [sb] vi (talk, have a discussion with)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 交谈 jiāo tán TC Traditional Chinese 交談  
 -- Mary wants to improve her Spanish so that she can converse with anyone she meets.
 
converse n (opposite case)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 谈话 tán huà TC Traditional Chinese 談話  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 谈天 tán huà，tán tiān 
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 交谈 tán huà，jiāo tán TC Traditional Chinese 交談 
 -- If I believe one thing, she'll believe the converse.
 
converse adj (contrary, opposite)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 相反的 xiāng fǎn de  
 -- Randy wasn't willing to listen to converse opinions.

动词短语 
 
converse in [sth] vtr phrasal insep (talk in a given language)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 用...交谈  (语言)
 -- He did not speak Italian and her Spanish was poor so they conversed in English.

